31
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da jednostavno to hoćete nečete od tim mačina jednog dijela osobnosti čoveka.

32
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] I s druge strane, ja sam htio iskreirati jednog super junaka, jel?

33
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Poučen svim živim superinacima, supermenima, batmenima i mojim najdražem srebrnom letačem.

34
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, kad si ti, kad si ti zapravo to, kad je to, da promjera imam, 2014?

35
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] 2014.

36
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je prije, uf, dosta godina.

37
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stradio od 20-godišnjice.

38
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto što sam te htio pitati, kako si odlučio, to je zanimljivo, ti si poslan čovjek zapravo,

39
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] živiš od svog posla.

40
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, da, mali poduzetnik.

41
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, mali poduzetnik, imaš neku filmu.

42
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Obrtnik, obrt.

43
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš, jel tako, knjigovostini servis, nekakav koji plaćaš, sve je normalno, plaćaš porez, doprinose.

44
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima, bisti boys ima jednu stvar, I got the skills to pay the bills, eto.

45
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:36,000
